snippet.title: Police: 62 Students Arrested After Senior Prank At Teaneck High School

localized.description:
More than 60 students at Teaneck High School were arrested Thursday after police said they broke into the school for a senior class prank, greased doorknobs with Vaseline and urinated in the hallways. CBS 2's Weijia Jiang reports.
